This is to inform you that;
During F.Y 2014-15 the borrowing of the company were restructured under CDR package. Subsequently in FY 17-18 the package was restructured under the name Scheme for Sustainable Structuring of Stressed Assets 
AS per RBI guidelines the company became liable to pay right of recompense of which approval for payment of same was made in the Board Meeting.
